{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":880,"text":"I and my colleagues Art Aron\nand Lucy Brown and others,"},{"time":4552,"text":"have put 37 people who are madly in love\ninto a functional MRI brain scanner."},{"time":9133,"text":"17 who were happily in love,\n15 who had just been dumped,"},{"time":13030,"text":"and we're just starting\nour third experiment:"},{"time":15190,"text":"studying people who report\nthat they're still in love"},{"time":17720,"text":"after 10 to 25 years of marriage."},{"time":20000,"text":"So, this is the short story\nof that research."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24550,"text":"In the jungles of Guatemala,\nin Tikal, stands a temple."},{"time":29124,"text":"It was built by the grandest Sun King,\nof the grandest city-state,"},{"time":34115,"text":"of the grandest civilization\nof the Americas, the Mayas."},{"time":38765,"text":"His name was Jasaw Chan K'awiil."},{"time":41474,"text":"He stood over six feet tall."},{"time":43777,"text":"He lived into his 80s,"},{"time":45818,"text":"and he was buried beneath\nthis monument in 720 AD."},{"time":50178,"text":"And Mayan inscriptions proclaim\nthat he was deeply in love with his wife."},{"time":54258,"text":"So, he built a temple\nin her honor, facing his."},{"time":58119,"text":"And every spring and autumn,\nexactly at the equinox,"},{"time":62111,"text":"the sun rises behind his temple,"},{"time":64570,"text":"and perfectly bathes her temple\nwith his shadow."},{"time":69630,"text":"And as the sun sets\nbehind her temple in the afternoon,"},{"time":73405,"text":"it perfectly bathes\nhis temple with her shadow."},{"time":77413,"text":"After 1,300 years, these two lovers\nstill touch and kiss from their tomb."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84476,"text":"Around the world, people love."},{"time":86793,"text":"They sing for love, they dance for love,"},{"time":89561,"text":"they compose poems and stories about love."},{"time":92593,"text":"They tell myths and legends about love."},{"time":95192,"text":"They pine for love, they live for love,\nthey kill for love, and they die for love."},{"time":101042,"text":"As Walt Whitman once said,\n\"O I would stake all for you.\""},{"time":105787,"text":"Anthropologists have found evidence\nof romantic love in 170 societies."},{"time":110000,"text":"They've never found a society\nthat did not have it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114116,"text":"But love isn't always a happy experience."},{"time":116840,"text":"In one study of college students,\nthey asked a lot of questions about love,"},{"time":120763,"text":"but the two that stood out\nto me the most were:"},{"time":123726,"text":"\"Have you ever been rejected\nby somebody who you really loved?\""},{"time":128356,"text":"And the second question was:"},{"time":129797,"text":"\"Have you ever dumped somebody\nwho really loved you?\""},{"time":133613,"text":"And almost 95 percent of both men\nand women said yes to both."},{"time":138919,"text":"Almost nobody gets out of love alive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142528,"text":"So, before I start telling you\nabout the brain,"},{"time":145807,"text":"I want to read for you"},{"time":147291,"text":"what I think is the most powerful\nlove poem on Earth."},{"time":150000,"text":"There's other love poems that are,\nof course, just as good,"},{"time":152841,"text":"but I don't think this one\ncan be surpassed."},{"time":155437,"text":"It was told by an anonymous\nKwakiutl Indian of southern Alaska"},{"time":160148,"text":"to a missionary in 1896."},{"time":163637,"text":"And here it is."},{"time":164887,"text":"I've never had the opportunity\nto say it before."},{"time":168495,"text":"\"Fire runs through my body\nwith the pain of loving you."},{"time":172548,"text":"Pain runs through my body\nwith the fires of my love for you."},{"time":176640,"text":"Pain like a boil about to burst\nwith my love for you,"},{"time":180507,"text":"consumed by fire with my love for you."},{"time":183622,"text":"I remember what you said to me."},{"time":185752,"text":"I am thinking of your love for me."},{"time":187861,"text":"I am torn by your love for me."},{"time":190210,"text":"Pain and more pain --"},{"time":192172,"text":"where are you going with my love?"},{"time":194233,"text":"I am told you will go from here."},{"time":196033,"text":"I am told you will leave me here."},{"time":198500,"text":"My body is numb with grief."},{"time":200689,"text":"Remember what I said, my love."},{"time":202772,"text":"Goodbye, my love, goodbye.\""},{"time":206645,"text":"Emily Dickinson once wrote,\n\"Parting is all we need to know of hell.\""},{"time":212856,"text":"How many people have suffered"},{"time":214998,"text":"in all the millions of years\nof human evolution?"},{"time":218617,"text":"How many people around the world"},{"time":220776,"text":"are dancing with elation\nat this very minute?"},{"time":224133,"text":"Romantic love is one of the most powerful\nsensations on Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228377,"text":"So, several years ago,\nI decided to look into the brain"},{"time":231835,"text":"and study this madness."},{"time":234699,"text":"Our first study of people\nwho were happily in love"},{"time":237300,"text":"has been widely publicized,"},{"time":238665,"text":"so I'm only going to say\nvery little about it."},{"time":241183,"text":"We found activity in a tiny,\nlittle factory near the base of the brain"},{"time":245187,"text":"called the ventral tegmental area."},{"time":247357,"text":"We found activity in some cells\ncalled the A10 cells,"},{"time":250525,"text":"cells that actually make\ndopamine, a natural stimulant,"},{"time":253478,"text":"and spray it to many brain regions."},{"time":255778,"text":"Indeed, this part, the VTA,\nis part of the brain's reward system."},{"time":259913,"text":"It's way below your cognitive\nthinking process."},{"time":262510,"text":"It's below your emotions."},{"time":264125,"text":"It's part of what we call\nthe reptilian core of the brain,"},{"time":267378,"text":"associated with wanting, with motivation,\nwith focus and with craving."},{"time":272648,"text":"In fact, the same brain region\nwhere we found activity"},{"time":275778,"text":"becomes active also\nwhen you feel the rush of cocaine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279651,"text":"But romantic love is much more\nthan a cocaine high --"},{"time":282618,"text":"at least you come down from cocaine."},{"time":284953,"text":"Romantic love is an obsession,\nit possesses you."},{"time":288258,"text":"You lose your sense of self."},{"time":289941,"text":"You can't stop thinking\nabout another human being."},{"time":293333,"text":"Somebody is camping in your head."},{"time":295750,"text":"As an eighth-century Japanese poet said,\n\"My longing had no time when it ceases.\""},{"time":302350,"text":"Wild is love."},{"time":304683,"text":"And the obsession can get worse\nwhen you've been rejected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308295,"text":"So, right now, Lucy Brown and I,\nthe neuroscientists on our project,"},{"time":313000,"text":"are looking at the data of the people"},{"time":315001,"text":"who were put into the machine\nafter they had just been dumped."},{"time":318356,"text":"It was very difficult actually,\nputting these people in the machine,"},{"time":321581,"text":"because they were in such bad shape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323340,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"So anyway, we found activity\nin three brain regions."},{"time":329643,"text":"We found activity in the brain region,"},{"time":332138,"text":"in exactly the same brain region\nassociated with intense romantic love."},{"time":336753,"text":"What a bad deal."},{"time":338653,"text":"You know, when you've been dumped,"},{"time":340325,"text":"the one thing you love to do\nis just forget about this human being,"},{"time":343546,"text":"and then go on with your life --\nbut no, you just love them harder."},{"time":347595,"text":"As the poet Terence,\nthe Roman poet once said,"},{"time":351187,"text":"he said, \"The less my hope,\nthe hotter my love.\""},{"time":354228,"text":"And indeed, we now know why."},{"time":356488,"text":"Two thousand years later,\nwe can explain this in the brain."},{"time":359730,"text":"That brain system -- the reward system"},{"time":362153,"text":"for wanting, for motivation,\nfor craving, for focus --"},{"time":366000,"text":"becomes more active\nwhen you can't get what you want."},{"time":369486,"text":"In this case, life's greatest prize:\nan appropriate mating partner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374270,"text":"We found activity\nin other brain regions also --"},{"time":377052,"text":"in a brain region associated\nwith calculating gains and losses."},{"time":381968,"text":"You're lying there,\nyou're looking at the picture,"},{"time":384339,"text":"and you're in this machine,"},{"time":385672,"text":"and you're calculating what went wrong."},{"time":387869,"text":"What have I lost?"},{"time":390441,"text":"As a matter of fact, Lucy and I\nhave a little joke about this."},{"time":394113,"text":"It comes from a David Mamet play,"},{"time":397000,"text":"and there's two con artists in the play,"},{"time":399098,"text":"and the woman is conning the man,"},{"time":401000,"text":"and the man looks at the woman and says,"},{"time":403205,"text":"\"Oh, you're a bad pony,\nI'm not going to bet on you.\""},{"time":408181,"text":"And indeed, it's this part of the brain,"},{"time":410775,"text":"the core of the nucleus accumbens,"},{"time":412705,"text":"that is becoming active\nas you're measuring your gains and losses."},{"time":416327,"text":"It's also the brain region\nthat becomes active"},{"time":418697,"text":"when you're willing to take enormous risks\nfor huge gains and huge losses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423618,"text":"Last but not least,\nwe found activity in a brain region"},{"time":426904,"text":"associated with deep attachment\nto another individual."},{"time":431583,"text":"No wonder people suffer around the world,\nand we have so many crimes of passion."},{"time":437730,"text":"When you've been rejected in love,"},{"time":439870,"text":"not only are you engulfed\nwith feelings of romantic love,"},{"time":443823,"text":"but you're feeling deep\nattachment to this individual."},{"time":446601,"text":"Moreover, this brain circuit\nfor reward is working,"},{"time":449872,"text":"and you're feeling intense energy,\nintense focus, intense motivation"},{"time":455072,"text":"and the willingness to risk it all,\nto win life's greatest prize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461477,"text":"So, what have I learned\nfrom this experiment"},{"time":464395,"text":"that I would like to tell the world?"},{"time":466141,"text":"Foremost, I have come to think"},{"time":468543,"text":"that romantic love is a drive,\na basic mating drive."},{"time":471989,"text":"Not the sex drive --"},{"time":473189,"text":"the sex drive gets you looking\nfor a whole range of partners."},{"time":476083,"text":"Romantic love enables you\nto focus your mating energy"},{"time":478613,"text":"on just one at a time,\nconserve your mating energy,"},{"time":481435,"text":"and start the mating process\nwith this single individual."},{"time":485117,"text":"I think of all the poetry\nthat I've read about romantic love,"},{"time":488758,"text":"what sums it up best\nis something that is said by Plato"},{"time":492604,"text":"over 2,000 years ago."},{"time":494731,"text":"He said, \"The god of love\nlives in a state of need."},{"time":498841,"text":"It is a need, it is an urge,\nit is a homeostatic imbalance."},{"time":504153,"text":"Like hunger and thirst,\nit's almost impossible to stamp out.\""},{"time":509081,"text":"I've also come to believe\nthat romantic love is an addiction:"},{"time":512392,"text":"a perfectly wonderful addiction\nwhen it's going well,"},{"time":514963,"text":"and a perfectly horrible addiction\nwhen it's going poorly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518059,"text":"And indeed, it has all\nof the characteristics of addiction."},{"time":520871,"text":"You focus on the person,\nyou obsessively think about them,"},{"time":524248,"text":"you crave them, you distort reality,"},{"time":527000,"text":"your willingness to take enormous\nrisks to win this person."},{"time":530324,"text":"And it's got the three main\ncharacteristics of addiction:"},{"time":533035,"text":"tolerance, you need to see them\nmore, and more, and more;"},{"time":535740,"text":"withdrawals;"},{"time":537301,"text":"and last: relapse."},{"time":538723,"text":"I've got a girlfriend who's just\ngetting over a terrible love affair."},{"time":542373,"text":"It's been about eight months,\nshe's beginning to feel better."},{"time":545280,"text":"And she was driving along\nin her car the other day,"},{"time":547770,"text":"and suddenly she heard a song\non the car radio"},{"time":549962,"text":"that reminded her of this man."},{"time":551421,"text":"Not only did the instant\ncraving come back,"},{"time":554308,"text":"but she had to pull over\nfrom the side of the road and cry."},{"time":558374,"text":"So, one thing I would like\nthe medical community,"},{"time":560765,"text":"and the legal community,\nand even the college community,"},{"time":563488,"text":"to see if they can understand,\nthat indeed, romantic love"},{"time":567325,"text":"is one of the most addictive\nsubstances on Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570415,"text":"I would also like to tell the world\nthat animals love."},{"time":574134,"text":"There's not an animal on this planet"},{"time":576329,"text":"that will copulate with anything\nthat comes along."},{"time":578749,"text":"Too old, too young, too scruffy,\ntoo stupid, and they won't do it."},{"time":583470,"text":"Unless you're stuck\nin a laboratory cage --"},{"time":586000,"text":"and you know, if you spend\nyour entire life in a little box,"},{"time":589720,"text":"you're not going to be as picky\nabout who you have sex with,"},{"time":593000,"text":"but I've looked in a hundred species,"},{"time":595901,"text":"and everywhere in the wild,\nanimals have favorites."},{"time":599000,"text":"As a matter of fact,\nethologists know this."},{"time":601027,"text":"There are over eight words\nfor what they call \"animal favoritism:\""},{"time":605000,"text":"selective proceptivity, mate choice,\nfemale choice, sexual choice."},{"time":610513,"text":"And indeed, there are now\nthree academic articles"},{"time":613513,"text":"in which they've looked\nat this attraction,"},{"time":616000,"text":"which may only last for a second,"},{"time":618000,"text":"but it's a definite attraction,"},{"time":619735,"text":"and either this same brain region,\nthis reward system,"},{"time":623041,"text":"or the chemicals of that reward\nsystem are involved."},{"time":626618,"text":"In fact, I think animal attraction\ncan be instant --"},{"time":629256,"text":"you can see an elephant\ninstantly go for another elephant."},{"time":632000,"text":"And I think that this is really the origin"},{"time":634024,"text":"of what you and I call\n\"love at first sight.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":638458,"text":"People have often asked me"},{"time":640578,"text":"whether what I know about love\nhas spoiled it for me."},{"time":644606,"text":"And I just simply say, \"Hardly.\""},{"time":646640,"text":"You can know every single ingredient\nin a piece of chocolate cake,"},{"time":649789,"text":"and then when you sit down\nand eat that cake,"},{"time":652508,"text":"you can still feel that joy."},{"time":654351,"text":"And certainly, I make all the same\nmistakes that everybody else does too,"},{"time":658033,"text":"but it's really deepened my understanding"},{"time":662296,"text":"and compassion, really,\nfor all human life."},{"time":666246,"text":"As a matter of fact, in New York,\nI often catch myself"},{"time":669519,"text":"looking in baby carriages\nand feeling a little sorry for the tot."},{"time":673104,"text":"And in fact, sometimes\nI feel a little sorry"},{"time":676000,"text":"for the chicken on my dinner plate,"},{"time":678023,"text":"when I think of how intense\nthis brain system is."},{"time":683231,"text":"Our newest experiment has been hatched"},{"time":687940,"text":"by my colleague, Art Aron --"},{"time":690618,"text":"putting people who are reporting\nthat they are still in love,"},{"time":693803,"text":"in a long-term relationship,\ninto the functional MRI."},{"time":696965,"text":"We've put five people in so far,"},{"time":699342,"text":"and indeed, we found exactly\nthe same thing."},{"time":702422,"text":"They're not lying."},{"time":703787,"text":"The brain areas associated\nwith intense romantic love"},{"time":709794,"text":"still become active, 25 years later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714556,"text":"There are still many questions\nto be answered"},{"time":717000,"text":"and asked about romantic love."},{"time":719770,"text":"The question that I'm working on\nright this minute --"},{"time":722309,"text":"and I'm only going to say it\nfor a second, and then end --"},{"time":725074,"text":"is, why do you fall in love\nwith one person, rather than another?"},{"time":728173,"text":"I never would have\neven thought to think of this,"},{"time":731000,"text":"but Match.com, the Internet dating site,"},{"time":733000,"text":"came to me three years ago\nand asked me that question."},{"time":735819,"text":"And I said, I don't know."},{"time":737168,"text":"I know what happens in the brain,\nwhen you do become in love,"},{"time":740569,"text":"but I don't know why you fall in love\nwith one person rather than another."},{"time":744110,"text":"And so, I've spent\nthe last three years on this."},{"time":746896,"text":"And there are many reasons\nthat you fall in love with one person"},{"time":749932,"text":"rather than another,\nthat psychologists can tell you."},{"time":752447,"text":"And we tend to fall in love with somebody\nfrom the same socioeconomic background,"},{"time":756304,"text":"the same general level of intelligence,\nof good looks, the same religious values."},{"time":760162,"text":"Your childhood certainly plays a role,\nbut nobody knows how."},{"time":763000,"text":"And that's about it, that's all they know."},{"time":765185,"text":"No, they've never found"},{"time":766819,"text":"the way two personalities\nfit together to make a good relationship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771202,"text":"So, it began to occur to me"},{"time":773000,"text":"that maybe your biology pulls you\ntowards some people rather than another."},{"time":778072,"text":"And I have concocted a questionnaire\nto see to what degree"},{"time":782632,"text":"you express dopamine, serotonin,\nestrogen and testosterone."},{"time":787000,"text":"I think we've evolved four\nvery broad personality types"},{"time":790295,"text":"associated with the ratios\nof these four chemicals in the brain."},{"time":794418,"text":"And on this dating site\nthat I have created, called Chemistry.com,"},{"time":798643,"text":"I ask you first a series of questions"},{"time":802276,"text":"to see to what degree\nyou express these chemicals,"},{"time":805433,"text":"and I'm watching who chooses who to love."},{"time":809000,"text":"And 3.7 million people have taken\nthe questionnaire in America."},{"time":813432,"text":"About 600,000 people have taken it\nin 33 other countries."},{"time":817818,"text":"I'm putting the data together now,"},{"time":819522,"text":"and at some point --\nthere will always be magic to love,"},{"time":822866,"text":"but I think I will come closer\nto understanding"},{"time":826305,"text":"why it is you can walk into a room\nand everybody is from your background,"},{"time":830606,"text":"your same general level\nof intelligence, good looks,"},{"time":834158,"text":"and you don't feel\npulled towards all of them."},{"time":836370,"text":"I think there's biology to that."},{"time":838273,"text":"I think we're going to end up,\nin the next few years,"},{"time":840858,"text":"to understand all kinds\nof brain mechanisms"},{"time":843072,"text":"that pull us to one person\nrather than another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846406,"text":"So, I will close with this."},{"time":848823,"text":"These are my older people."},{"time":851939,"text":"Faulkner said, \"The past is not dead,\nit's not even past.\""},{"time":857431,"text":"Indeed, we carry a lot of luggage\nfrom our yesteryear in the human brain."},{"time":862412,"text":"And so, there's one thing that makes me\npursue my understanding of human nature,"},{"time":869777,"text":"and this reminds me of it."},{"time":871802,"text":"These are two women."},{"time":873250,"text":"Women tend to get intimacy\ndifferently than men do."},{"time":876406,"text":"Women get intimacy\nfrom face-to-face talking."},{"time":878690,"text":"We swivel towards each other,"},{"time":880611,"text":"we do what we call\nthe \"anchoring gaze\" and we talk."},{"time":884737,"text":"This is intimacy to women."},{"time":886324,"text":"I think it comes from millions of years"},{"time":888233,"text":"of holding that baby\nin front of your face,"},{"time":890339,"text":"cajoling it, reprimanding it,\neducating it with words."},{"time":893773,"text":"Men tend to get intimacy\nfrom side-by-side doing."},{"time":897390,"text":"As soon as one guy looks up,\nthe other guy will look away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900784,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":902507,"text":"I think it comes from millions of years\nsitting behind the bush,"},{"time":907628,"text":"looking straight ahead, trying to hit\nthat buffalo on the head with a rock."},{"time":912099,"text":"I think, for millions of years,\nmen faced their enemies,"},{"time":914890,"text":"they sat side-by-side with friends."},{"time":917642,"text":"So my final statement is: love is in us."},{"time":921918,"text":"It's deeply embedded in the brain."},{"time":924510,"text":"Our challenge is to understand each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927339,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":928564,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}